BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 202.32 740 Td (UNDERSTANDING CHILD ANXIETY) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 730 m 562 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 50 705 Td (Anxiety is the #1 mental health issue in children \(affects 1 in 8\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 50 685 Td (It's NOT something kids grow out of without help.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 50 655 Td (TYPES OF CHILDHOOD ANXIETY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 60 630 Td (Separation anxiety:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 210 630 Td (Fear of being away from parents) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 60 610 Td (Social anxiety:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 210 610 Td (Fear of judgment, embarrassment, peers) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 60 590 Td (Generalized anxiety:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 210 590 Td (Worry about everything \(grades, health, safety\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 60 570 Td (Specific phobias:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 210 570 Td (Intense fear of specific things \(dogs, storms, needles\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 60 550 Td (Selective mutism:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 210 550 Td (Can't speak in certain settings despite talking at home) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 520 Td (SIGNS YOUR CHILD MAY HAVE ANXIETY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 500 Td (- Frequent stomachaches/headaches) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 484 Td (- Avoids new situations or activities) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 468 Td (- Asks 'what if' questions constantly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 452 Td (- Cries, clings, or has meltdowns before events) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 436 Td (- Has trouble sleeping or needs you present to sleep) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 420 Td (- Seeks constant reassurance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 404 Td (- Is a perfectionist) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 388 Td (- Has outbursts that seem disproportionate) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
